## Architecture Diagram

```mermaid
graph TB
    subgraph "UI Layer (Streamlit)"
        APP["app.py<br/>Router + Sidebar"]
        AUTH["views/auth.py"]
        DASH["views/dashboard.py"]
        BOT["views/bot_management.py"]
        CHAT["views/chat.py"]
        SETT["views/settings.py"]
    end

    subgraph "AI / RAG Layer"
        RAG["rag_engine.py<br/>Vision RAG Pipeline"]
        GW["llm_gateway.py<br/>Multi-Provider Adapter"]
        IR["intent_router.py<br/>Keyword Classifier"]
    end

    subgraph "Data Layer"
        DB["database.py<br/>SQLite CRUD"]
        VS["vector_store.py<br/>ChromaDB Client"]
        ENC["encryption.py<br/>Fernet AES-256"]
    end

    subgraph "Storage"
        SQLITE[("chatbot.db")]
        CHROMA[("chroma_data/")]
        ASSETS["document_assets/"]
        ENV[".env<br/>GOOGLE_API_KEY<br/>MASTER_KEY"]
    end

    subgraph "External APIs"
        GEMINI["Google Gemini<br/>Vision + Embedding"]
        OPENAI_API["OpenAI API"]
        ANTHRO["Anthropic API"]
    end

    APP --> AUTH & DASH & BOT & CHAT & SETT
    BOT -->|upload| RAG
    CHAT -->|query| RAG
    CHAT --> IR
    CHAT --> GW
    RAG --> VS
    RAG --> DB
    RAG -->|server key| GEMINI
    GW -->|user BYOK key| GEMINI & OPENAI_API & ANTHRO
    SETT --> ENC --> DB
    DB --> SQLITE
    VS --> CHROMA
    RAG --> ASSETS
    ENC --> ENV
    RAG --> ENV
```
